data.short_description: Resuming the session after switching to Discord from another app spams the debug log with ZipExceptions
data.steps_to_repro: - (optional) Kill Discord to clear the debug log, and ensure that no error is shown already - Either minimize Discord using Home button and open another app, or open a link from Discord in order to open YouTube, Trello, etc. Either way, do NOT kill the app, leave it running in background - Go back to Discord and check debug log
